<div
  data-particle_enable="false"
  data-particle-mobile-disabled="false"
  class="elementor-element elementor-element-2572779 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child"
  data-id="2572779"
  data-element_type="container"
>
  <div
    data-particle_enable="false"
    data-particle-mobile-disabled="false"
    class="elementor-element elementor-element-ffaacca e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child"
    data-id="ffaacca"
    data-element_type="container"
  >
    <div
      class="elementor-element elementor-element-b065a01 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading"
      data-id="b065a01"
      data-element_type="widget"
      data-widget_type="heading.default"
    >
      <div class="elementor-widget-container">
        <h2 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">
          Military Service &amp; Veterans Overview
        </h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="elementor-element elementor-element-34dede2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor"
      data-id="34dede2"
      data-element_type="widget"
      data-widget_type="text-editor.default"
    >
      <div class="elementor-widget-container">
        <p>
          <strong
            >Honoring Service. Understanding Sacrifice. Inspiring
            Leadership.</strong
          >
        </p>
        <p>&nbsp;</p>
        <p>
          The <strong>Military Service &amp; Veterans Badge</strong> invites
          Scouts to explore the values, history, and human stories behind
          military service. Designed to deepen understanding and foster respect,
          this badge connects Scouts with the heritage of our Armed Forces and
          the individuals who have served our nation with courage and
          commitment.
        </p>
        <p>&nbsp;</p>
        <p>
          Through hands-on learning, meaningful conversations, and active
          community involvement, Scouts develop a richer appreciation for
          service, leadership, peace, and patriotism.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div
