    <div class="elementor-widget-container">
      <p>
        <strong
          >You decide if this activity becomes an official Merit Badge of
          Scouting America.</strong
        >&nbsp; By filling out the survey, you vote for or against this becoming
        a Merit Badge.&nbsp; You can also suggest changes to make the merit
        badge more engaging.&nbsp; The fate of this potential merit badge rests
        in your hands.&nbsp; Come back and complete the survey after you finish
        the requirements to make your voice heard and to get your certificate of
        completion.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
